title: Zoner.Mobile.Security.Tablet.Paid.Apk
description: Zoner Mobile Security is a modern security and anti-virus solution for your device. It provides protection against viruses, trojans, worms, spyware, adware and other malware as well as phone call and message protection. This product has been developed in Europe where many good Anti-Virus products like AVG, Avast, ESET, Avira, and Kaspersky come from. Additional Features : Theft Protection (find and control your missing device). Installed App protection. On-access and on demand scan. Phone filtering (block calls and messages). Parental lock for calls. Permission viewer. Has a task manager. Automatic and manual database updates. Home screen widget. And You can secure messages. Enjoy and re-seed please!
